#: templates/activate.html:5
msgid ""
"The activation key {{ activation_key }} is invalid and cannot be used to "
"activate this account."
msgstr ""
"De activatie sleutel {{ activation_key }} is ongeldig en kan niet gebruikt "
"worden om dit account te activeren."

#: templates/activation_complete.html:5
msgid "Your account is activated now!"
msgstr "Uw account is geactiveerd!"

#: templates/activation_email.txt:2
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Hello,\n"
"\n"
"Someone, hopefully you, signed up for a new account at %(site)s using this "
"email address. If it was you, and you'd like to activate and use your "
"account, click the link below or copy and paste it into your web browser's "
"address bar:\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Goedendag,\n"
"\n"
"Iemand heeft een account aangemaakt voor deze %(site)s met dit "
"email adres. Als u dit was dan kunt u uw account activeren door op onderstaande "
"link te klikken. U kunt ook de link kopieren en in de adres bar van uw webbrowser "
"plakken:\n"

#: templates/activation_email.txt:10
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"If you didn't request this, you don't need to do anything; you won't receive "
"any more email from us, and the account will expire automatically in "
"%(expiration_days)s days.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Als u geen nieuw account heeft aangemaakt dan hoeft u niets te doen. U krijgt geen "
"email meer van ons en het account wordt automatisch verwijderd in "
"%(expiration_days)s dagen.\n"

#: templates/activation_email_subject.txt:2
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Activate your %(site)s account - you have %(expiration_days)s days!\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Activeer uw %(site)s account - u heeft %(expiration_days)s dagen!\n"

#: templates/login.html:8
msgid "Jarrbo login"
msgstr "Jarrbo login"

#: templates/login.html:15
msgid ""
"You don&#39t have an account? You can create an account using the button "
"below."
msgstr ""
"Heeft u geen account? U kunt er één aanmaken met onderstaande button."

#: templates/login.html:21
msgid ""
"Forgotten your password? Enter your email address below, and we&#39ll email "
"instructions for setting a new one"
msgstr ""
"Wachtwoord vergeten? Vul uw email adres hieronder in en we mailen u instructies "
"om een nieuw wachtwoord aan te maken."

#: templates/login.html:23 templates/password_reset_form.html:5
#: templates/password_reset_form.html:16
msgid "Reset my password"
msgstr "Wachtwoord resetten"

#: templates/logout.html:5
msgid "You've been logged out."
msgstr "U bent uitgelogd"

#: templates/logout.html:6
msgid "Login again."
msgstr "Opnieuw inloggen"

#: templates/password_change_done.html:6
msgid "Your password was changed."
msgstr "Uw wachtwoord is gewijzigd"

#: templates/password_change_form.html:8
msgid "Change Password"
msgstr "Wachtwoord wijzigen"

#: templates/password_reset_complete.html:7
msgid "Your password has been set.  You may go ahead and log in now."
msgstr "Uw wachtwoord is ingesteld. U kunt nu inloggen."

#: templates/password_reset_complete.html:10
msgid "Log in"
msgstr "Inloggen"

#: templates/password_reset_confirm.html:8
msgid ""
"Please enter your new password twice so we can verify you typed it in "
"correctly."
msgstr "Voer uw wachtwoord tweemaal in."

#: templates/password_reset_confirm.html:16
msgid "Change my password"
msgstr "Wijzig mijn wachtwoord"

#: templates/password_reset_confirm.html:25
msgid ""
"The password reset link was invalid, possibly because it has already been "
"used.  Please request a new password reset."
msgstr ""
"Deze wachtwoord reset link is niet geldig, waarschijnlijk omdat hij al "
"gebruikt is. Probeert u nogmaals een wachtwoord reset."

#: templates/password_reset_done.html:8
msgid ""
"We've emailed you instructions for setting your password, if an account "
"exists with the email you entered. You should receive them shortly."
msgstr ""
"Wij hebben u instructies gestuurd om uw wachtwoord in te stellen indien dit "
"account bestaat."

#: templates/password_reset_done.html:10
msgid ""
"If you don't receive an email, please make sure you've entered the address "
"you registered with, and check your spam folder."
msgstr ""
"Als u geen email ontvangt controleer dan uw spam folder."

#: templates/password_reset_email.txt:3
msgid "Dear user,"
msgstr "Beste gebruiker,"

#: templates/password_reset_email.txt:5
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You're receiving this email because you requested a password reset for your "
"user account at %(site_name)s."
msgstr ""
"U ontvangt deze mail omdat u een wachtwoord reset heeft aangevraagd voor uw account "
"bij %(site_name)s."

#: templates/password_reset_email.txt:7
msgid "Please go to the following page and choose a new password:"
msgstr "Ga naar de volgende link en kies een nieuw wachtwoord:"

#: templates/password_reset_email.txt:12
msgid "Thanks for using our site!"
msgstr "Bedankt voor het gebruiken van onze site!"

#: templates/password_reset_email.txt:14
#, python-format
msgid "The %(site_name)s team"
msgstr "%(site_name)s team"

#: templates/password_reset_form.html:7
msgid "Forgotten your password?"
msgstr "Wachtwoord vergeten?"

#: templates/password_reset_form.html:7
msgid ""
"Enter your email address below, and we'll email instructions for setting a "
"new one."
msgstr "" 
"Vul uw email adres hieronder in en wij sturen u instructies om een "
"nieuwe in te voeren"

#: templates/password_reset_subject.txt:2
#, python-format
msgid "Password reset on %(site_name)s"
msgstr "Wachtwoord reset voor %(site_name)s"

